<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Country-Bj on OONI: Open Observatory of Network Interference</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/tags/country-bj/</link><description>Recent content in Country-Bj on OONI: Open Observatory of Network Interference</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2019 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ooni.github.io/tags/country-bj/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Benin: Social media blocking and Internet blackout amid 2019 elections</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/post/2019-benin-social-media-blocking/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/post/2019-benin-social-media-blocking/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Two days ago, social media was &lt;a href="https://netblocks.org/reports/internet-blocked-in-benin-on-election-day-aAwqknyM"&gt;reportedly&lt;/a&gt; blocked and access to the Internet was shutdown in Benin during its 2019 parliamentary elections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this report, the &lt;a href="https://ooni.io/"&gt;Open Observatory of Network Interference (OONI)&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href="https://www.caida.org/"&gt;Center for Applied Internet Data Analysis (CAIDA)&lt;/a&gt; teams share &lt;a href="https://api.ooni.io/files/by_country/BJ"&gt;OONI&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://ioda.caida.org/ioda/dashboard#view=inspect&amp;amp;entity=country/BJ&amp;amp;lastView=overview&amp;amp;from=1556385008&amp;amp;until=1556557928"&gt;IODA&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="https://atlas.ripe.net/"&gt;RIPE Atlas&lt;/a&gt; network measurement data that corroborate and provide insight into these recent censorship events in Benin.&lt;/p&gt;
